Subject: Application for Office Leave

Dear [Manager's Name],

I am writing to request a [number] day leave from [start date] to [end date] due to personal reasons. I would like to take this opportunity to attend to some family and personal matters that require my attention.

I have made sure to review our team's schedule and tasks, and I have made arrangements to ensure a smooth transition of my responsibilities while I am away. My colleagues, [names of team members], will be able to handle any urgent matters that may arise during my absence.

During my leave, I will ensure that all my tasks are up to date and completed before I leave. I will also be available by email if any urgent matters arise and will respond as soon as possible.

I would like to request your approval for this leave and would be grateful if you could let me know if there are any issues or concerns. I will make sure to catch up on any missed work and respond to any emails or messages as soon as possible upon my return.

The details of my leave are as follows:

* Start date: [start date]
* End date: [end date]
* Number of days: [number] days
* Reason for leave: Personal reasons

I would like to request for the following documents to be processed for my leave:

* Leave approval letter
* Pay slip (if any)

Please let me know if there is any further information you need from me. I appreciate your understanding and approval of my leave request.

Thank you for your time and consideration.

Sincerely,

Aditya

[Your Signature]

Note: This is a sample application for office leave. Please adjust the details according to your requirements and company policies.

